SUMMARY:Mixed Media Face Cards Class
DESCRIPTION:Nancy Lorenz: The Elements			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n				\n									\n				\n				\n							\n		\n	\n\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n\n	\n		\n\nTurn ordinary playing cards into extraordinary miniature artworks in this creative mixed-media class!  \n\n\n\nUsing face cards as your canvas\, you’ll design and embellish a one-of-a-kind keepsake inspired by either a beach or garden theme.  \n\n\n\nLearn how to layer “bits and bobs” like beads\, ribbon\, wire\, charms\, and tiny miniatures to add texture\, dimension\, and personality to your piece. \n\n\n\nLeave with a beautifully finished keepsake ready to hang or display\, and the skills to create more at home! \n\n\n\nPlease note that the sample image shows examples of cards created by the instructor. Cards created in class will differ in style and theme. \n\n\n\nRegistration required.  \n\n\n\nMembers: $20 | General Public: $25 \n\n\n\nNot a Member? Join today and receive discounts on classes and camps\, exclusive invites to events\, and FREE reciprocal membership to the Virginia Museum of Fine Arts in Richmond\, among other perks! Click here to learn more and join. \n\n	\n\n\n\n	\n				\n			\n				\n			\n			\n				Add to Calendar\n								\n			\n		\n				\n			\n				\n					\n				\n			\n			\n				Driving? Get Directions\n			\n		\n		\n			\n				\n			\n			\n				Share  This!\n			\n		\n						\n			\n				\n			\n			\n				Register Now\n			\n		\n			\n	\n				\n		\n						\n				\n					\n						Date:					 \n					\n						\n							\n								\n									Feb 04\, 2027								\n								\n																											\n											May 16\, 2027
URL:https://www.taubmanmuseum.org/mixed-media-playing-cards
