SUMMARY:Material and Light: A Conversation with Artist Nancy Lorenz
DESCRIPTION:Nancy Lorenz: The Elements			\n		\n	\n\n\n\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n				\n									\n				\n				\n								\n					Nancy Lorenz\, Moonlight\, 2023\, silver leaf\, mother of pearl\, shellac\, pigment on wood panel\, 36 x 60 in.\, courtesy of the artist				\n							\n		\n	\n\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n\n	\n		\n\nGet an extra special sneak peek at an upcoming exhibition with artist Nancy Lorenz in advance of her solo exhibition\, The Elements\, opening February 2027 here at the Taubman Museum of Art. \n\n\n\nIn conversation with Curator Laura K. Higgins\, Lorenz will explore her distinctive practice\, which draws on a lifetime of engagement with rich materials and surface techniques.  \n\n\n\nLorenz’s luminous works—layered with gold\, silver\, and palladium leaf\, mother-of-pearl inlay\, resin\, and lacquer—reflect both Western abstraction and deep influence from traditional Japanese craft and aesthetics\, a sensibility first seeded during her formative years in Tokyo. \n\n\n\nPresented in dialogue with selections of Japanese prints and a kimono from the Museum’s Sharing Collection\, this program situates Lorenz’s material language within broader artistic and cultural lineages\, offering insight into the ideas and influences that will shape her forthcoming exhibition. \n\n\n\nMembers Free | General Public: $8 \n\n\n\nNot a Member? Join today and receive benefits such as discounts on classes and camps\, invitations to exclusive events\, free reciprocal membership to the Virginia Museum of Fine Arts in Richmond\, and more! Click here to learn more.  \n\n	\n\n\n\n	\n				\n			\n				\n			\n			\n				Add to Calendar\n								\n			\n		\n				\n			\n				\n					\n				\n			\n			\n				Driving? Get Directions\n			\n		\n		\n			\n				\n			\n			\n				Share  This!\n			\n		\n						\n			\n				\n			\n			\n				Register Now\n			\n		\n			\n	\n				\n		\n						\n				\n					\n						Date:					 \n					\n						\n							\n								\n									Feb 04\, 2027								\n								\n																											\n											May 16\, 2027
URL:https://www.taubmanmuseum.org/conversation-with-nancy-lorenz
LOCATION:Taubman Museum of Art\, 110 Salem Ave SE\, Roanoke\, VA\, 24011\, United States
CATEGORIES:Adults,Children & Family,Current Events,Upcoming Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.taubmanmuseum.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Nancy-Lorenz-Moonlight_36x60.jpg
END:VEVENT
